%b%N%b allows users to request and use virtual hosts
or usercloaks. The following commands allow users to
maintain their virtual hosts; to use them, type
%b/msg %N <command>%b. For more information on a
specific command, type %b/msg %N help <command>%b.

    ON         Enables your virtualhost.
    OFF        Disables your virtualhost.
%+a    SET        Sets a user's virtualhost.
